            <h1>Spatio-temporal flow variations driving heat exchange processes at a mountain glacier</h1>
            <div class="auto-fixed-top-forced article-title">
                <div class="grid-container show-on-fixed" style="display: none">
                    <div class="grid-85 mobile-grid-85 tablet-grid-85 grid-parent">
                        <span class="d-block hide-on-mobile hide-on-tablet journal-contentHeaderColor">Spatio-temporal flow variations driving heat exchange processes at a mountain glacier</span>
