                                                     Mott, R., Stiperski, I., and Nicholson, L.: Spatio-temporal flow variations driving heat exchange processes at a mountain glacier, The Cryosphere, 14, 4699&ndash;4718, https://doi.org/10.5194/tc-14-4699-2020, 2020.
